OL,3,CCouncil scraps plan to cut hundreds of
OL,4,Cgritting routes after backlash
OL,6,FPlans by Calderdale Council to cut
OL,7,Fhundreds of roads from routine winter
OL,8,Fgritting rounds have been scrapped
OL,9,Ffollowing a public backlash.
OL,11,FThe council had proposed drastically
OL,12,Freducing the number of streets it
OL,13,Fgritted as a precaution during cold
OL,14,Fweather to save money.
OL,16,FBut it said it had "listened carefully
OL,17,Fto the large number of concerns
OL,18,Fexpressed ahead of the changes and has
OL,19,Ftaken action".
