OL,3,CCouncil scraps plan to cut hundreds of
OL,4,Cgritting routes after backlash
OL,6,FCouncil leader Jane Scullion said: "We
OL,7,Fpride ourselves on keeping people
OL,8,Fsafe, whilst also balancing our budget
OL,9,Fin tough times as we must do legally.
OL,11,F"We will think again, consider what
OL,12,Fother ways we can achieve these
OL,13,Fsavings, and put these options to all
OL,14,Fcouncillors to consider when we launch
OL,15,Four proposed budget in the new year."
OL,17,FThe Labour-run council announced last
OL,18,Fmonth that it would reduce the number
OL,19,Fof precautionary gritting routes it
OL,20,Fcovered to save #300,000 from its
OL,21,F#1.7million winter services budget.
