OL,3,CCouncil scraps plan to cut hundreds of
OL,4,Cgritting routes after backlash
OL,6,FIt said it would prioritise busy
OL,7,Froads, routes needed by emergency
OL,8,Fservices and roads that provided
OL,9,Faccess to community facilities such as
OL,10,Fhospitals, schools and town centres.
OL,12,FUnder the plans, hundreds of other
OL,13,Fstreets would not be routinely
OL,14,Fgritted. Signs were installed in
OL,15,Faffected areas.
OL,17,FBut residents told ITV News the move
OL,18,Fwas dangerous and could have
OL,19,F"terrible" consequences.
