OL,3,CCouncil scraps plan to cut hundreds of
OL,4,Cgritting routes after backlash
OL,6,FThe council's cabinet member for
OL,7,Ftransport, Cllr Sarah Courtney, said
OL,8,Fwork to find other "efficiencies"
OL,9,Fwould continue "to maximise our scarce
OL,10,Fresources".
OL,12,F"We recognise these actions will not
OL,13,Faddress the financial pressures caused
OL,14,Fby delivering our current winter
OL,15,Fservice in Calderdale, with its steep-
OL,16,Fsided hills and valleys," she said.
