OL,6,F"This means we will need to consider
OL,7,Ffurther alternative savings, at an
OL,8,Funprecedented and difficult time for
OL,9,Flocal councils, as we set the council
OL,10,Fbudget next year."
OL,12,FThe council will write to all
OL,13,Fhouseholds affected over the next week.
